<section class="section" aria-labelledby="story-heading">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div style="max-width:var(--content-width);margin:0 auto;">
      <h2 id="story-heading" style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:var(--text-xl);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);color:var(--text-primary);">Our Story</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);">Best Practice Flooring LLC was built on a simple idea: homeowners deserve a flooring installer who treats their home like their own. We're Ake and Sarah — husband and wife, based in Independence, Oregon — and we bring that care to every project across the Mid-Willamette Valley.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:var(--space-lg);">Ake is a hands-on craftsman who installs every floor personally. He doesn't manage crews from an office — he's on your job site, measuring, cutting, and laying every plank and tile with the precision that only comes from doing the work yourself.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--text-secondary);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:var(--space-2xl);">Sarah manages the business side — scheduling, customer communication, and making sure your project stays on track and on budget. When you call Best Practice Flooring, you talk to us — not a call center, not a receptionist. Just the people who are going to take care of your home.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

